com.onenetwork.backchain.client

Class Dispute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onenetwork.backchain.client.Dispute

  • public class Dispute
extends java.lang.Object
    A Dispute captures a concern raised by a Backchain participant about a transaction or business transaction. Any participant can file a Dispute, and only that participant can "resolve" the Dispute.
